@Bharat, I have don't a fully testing for this idea, but it could work for the potential resizable master scenario. Because based on my design, the list availability_zone_list_for_multi_masters will be generated at the template_def level, in other words, it will be made by python code, so we do have the capability to get whatever list we want.

